So everyone knows the value of playtesting, right?

18
00:01:03,883 --> 00:01:05,746
You've got a game, and you're sure players

19
00:01:05,786 --> 00:01:07,368
are going to act in a particular way.

20
00:01:07,388 --> 00:01:09,291
And then you throw real people at it,

21
