And for that, I'll be using my and Scopely's latest game, the Looney Tunes World of Mayhem.

45
00:02:23,364 --> 00:02:27,166
So this is an RPG battler where you collect characters,

46
00:02:27,446 --> 00:02:31,729
level them up, and battle other players and PvE enemies alike.

47
00:02:32,229 --> 00:02:37,052
there's a ton of different materials that you need to tune up your characters and unlock better

48
00:02:37,092 --> 00:02:43,036
skills. That's actually about all you need to know to follow along today, but the game is a

